How To Star And HiSat

STAR
/home/proj/biosoft/software/STAR_2.3.0e.Linux_x86_64/STAR --runThreadN 16 --genomeDir /home/proj/biosoft/praktikum/genprakt/assignments/a2/data/star_index --readFilesIn forwardReads.fastq reverseReads.fastq

HISAT
/home/proj/biosoft/software/hisat-0.1.6-beta/hisat -p 16 -x /home/proj/biosoft/praktikum/genprakt-ws16/assignment/a2/data/hisat_index -1 forwardReads.fastq -2 reverseReads.fastq -S fileToWriteSAMoutputTo

link to hisat-manual: https://ccb.jhu.edu/software/hisat/manual.shtml#running-hisat

SORT SAM files
/home/proj/biosoft/software/samtools-0.1.19/samtools view -uS Aligned.out.sam | /home/proj/biosoft/software/samtools-0.1.19/samtools sort -n Aligned.out.sorted.bam